summary: Mother of Super Eagles forward Samuel Kalu set free by kidnappers
title: Mother of Super Eagles forward Samuel Kalu set free by kidnappers
body:
Mother of Super Eagles forward Samuel Kalu set free by kidnappers

But according to Police in Abia State, the footballer’s mum has been released although it is known if the ransom was paid. 

It’s good news for Super Eagles star Samuel Kalu whose mother has been set free by kidnappers who held her for almost a week. 

Mrs Ozuruonye Juliet Kalu was on Wednesday, February 27 abducted by some unidentified gunmen along Okpulu Umuobo area of Aba in Abia State, Nigeria.

summary: Super Eagles striker Anthony Nwaekeme bags brace for Trabzonspor against Kasimpasa in Turkey
title: Super Eagles striker Anthony Nwaekeme bags brace for Trabzonspor against Kasimpasa in Turkey
body:
Super Eagles striker Anthony Nwaekeme bags brace for Trabzonspor against Kasimpasa in Turkey

Watch Anthony Nnaduzor Nwakaeme score two goals as Trabzonspor played out a 2-2 draw with Kasimpasa

Super Eagles striker Anthony Nwaekeme scored a brace for Trabzonspor in their 2-2 draw against Kasimpasa on Monday, March 4.

Nwaekeme who moved to Trabzonspor from Hapoel B e’er Sheva in the summer of 2018 has struggled to recreate his goalscoring heroics he was known for during his time in Isreal.
